User's privacy policy is very important to us. By using Silent Eye, you agree to the following policies:

Camera:
   On wrong password, PIN or pattern,Silent Eye uses the camera permission to take pictures. This will not take any picture other time. The pictures stored
   only in your device. Silent Eye is in accordance with the Official User Data Policy For Google API Service.
   
   
 Changes to this Privacy Policy: 
    We may update our Privacy Policy for time to time. Thus, you are advised to review this page periodically for any changes. We will notify you of any 
    changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. These changes are effective immediately after they are posted on this page.
